      <li>‚úÖ Total testosterone 200-400 ng/dL</li>
      <li>‚úÖ Needle-phobic</li>
      <li>‚úÖ Want to avoid shutdown/PCT</li>
      <li>‚úÖ Prefer natural production over replacement</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="vs-card">
