<h2>Can You Switch Between Them?</h2>

<p><strong>Yes!</strong> Many men try enclomiphene first, then switch to traditional TRT if:</p>

<ul style="margin: 24px 0;">
  <li>Enclomiphene doesn't raise testosterone enough (non-responders)</li>
  <li>Side effects are problematic (vision changes, mood swings)</li>
  <li>They finish having kids and want maximum optimization</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Switching is easy:</strong> Simply stop enclomiphene and start TRT. No wash-out period needed.</p>

